- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category as the paper evaluates the proposed algorithm on machine learning models and datasets.
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is a possible category as the paper deals with attacking NLP models and cloud services.
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is a less likely category as the paper does not explicitly deal with image or video data, but the proposed algorithm could potentially be applied to text in images or videos.
